  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 440333c5586acf44db3ff057db103969, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 1 Daughter Messages
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08a894b9b170bd4408c3738b6b563b07, type: 2}
  lines:
  - "I assume you\u2019ve heard the radio broadcast already, but just wanted to let
    you know that I\u2019m having to stay down here until my evac."
  - "It looks like I\u2019m quite low priority on the list so I\u2019ll still be
    here for quite a few days at least."
  - Oh, and I did hear from one of wives of your coworkers at the orphanage about
    the whole evacuation helping thing.
  - Good luck with it! It sounds stressful, but helping everyone stay safe from this
    whole thing must be a good motivator!
  - Glad to see the government handling this all so well.
  - "I don\u2019t have much time to talk anymore unfortunately, but do your best,
    and I look forward to seeing you when this is all over!!"
